# Frontend design — Listing & Claim Gate

## Identity: "Editorial Commerce Ledger"

Do **not** copy MasterFabric / reference-repo aesthetics (deep navy `#0b0f17`,
electric `#4f8cff`, monospace telemetry clone, MF badge chrome).

Use this system instead:

| Token | Value | Role |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Canvas | `#E8EEF2` + soft teal/amber washes | Cool stone, not cream |
| Surface | `#FFFFFF` / `#F4F7F9` | Cards |
| Ink | `#14181F` | Text |
| Accent | `#0F766E` teal | CTA / focus |
| Type | Fraunces (display) + DM Sans (UI) | Distinctive, not Inter |

Inspiration lane (study structure, do not copy assets): Awwwards / CSS Design
Awards commerce-ops and fintech dashboards — editorial type, clear hierarchy,
generous whitespace, one accent, decisive status color.

## Rules

- Responsive mobile-first; Gate stacks under `md`, splits on `md+`.
- Prefer `gap-*` stacks; pill CTAs OK for this brand (commerce soft).
- Status colors: PASS teal/green, REVIEW amber, REJECT rose — never purple glow.
- Illustrations only via `docs/ILLUSTRATIONS.md` master pack (updated palette).
- Empty states: one quiet panel + short copy; no decorative card grids.

## Anti-patterns

- Slate-on-navy instrument panels from academy sample repos
- Purple gradients, neon glow, glassmorphism stacks
- Warm cream + terracotta “AI default” landing looks
- Inset hero media cards on app shell screens
